metadata.name: Spaghetti
metadata.description:
An Italian dish served on a model who has recovered from anorexia. 

Anorexia nervosa is an illness that impacts women, men, adolescents, and children. It does not discriminate. It affects all ethnicities, cultures, and socioeconomic groups. It is also the deadliest mental illness, with a higher mortality rate than any other mental illness.
